@startuml AdminSec_UC02-00_Inscription
title UC-02-00: S-Inscrire - AdminSecretariat (Inscription + Choix Plan)

actor AdminSecretariat as A
participant Dashboard
participant Systeme
participant DB
participant Stripe
participant Logs

A -> Dashboard: 1. Accede page inscription
activate Dashboard

Dashboard --> A: 2. Affiche formulaire inscription (nom, email, mdp, nom secretariat)
deactivate Dashboard

A -> Dashboard: 3. Rempli formulaire et clique Suivant
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> Dashboard: 4. Valide format email et champs requis

alt Email invalide ou champs vides
  Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Format invalide
  Dashboard -> Logs: Log tentative inscription: Format invalide
  activate Logs
  Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue
  deactivate Logs
  deactivate Dashboard
else Donnees valides
  Dashboard -> Systeme: 5. Valide email unique dans systeme
  activate Systeme

  Systeme -> DB: 6. Verifie email non existe
  activate DB

  alt Email existe deja
    DB --> Systeme: ERREUR: Email existe
    deactivate DB
    Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR 400: Email deja utilise
    deactivate Systeme
    Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Email deja utilise
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Email unique OK
    DB --> Systeme: Email unique OK
    deactivate DB

    Systeme -> Systeme: 7. Genere hash mot de passe securise

    Systeme --> Dashboard: Validation OK
    deactivate Systeme

    Dashboard --> A: 8. Affiche selection plans avec tarifs (Basic, Pro, Enterprise)
    deactivate Dashboard

    A -> Dashboard: 9. Selectionne plan Pro (€XX TVAC/mois) et clique Continuer
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 10. Valide plan selectionne
    activate Systeme

    alt Plan invalide
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Plan invalide
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Plan inexistant
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Plan valide
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> DB: 11. Prepare creation compte (secretariat + admin)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Pret pour creation
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard --> A: 12. Affiche resume: Nom, Email, Plan, Montant initial TVAC
      deactivate Dashboard

      A -> Dashboard: 13. Clique Confirmer et Payer
      activate Dashboard

      Dashboard -> Stripe: 14. Appelle API Stripe CreateSubscription (plan, montant TVAC)
      activate Stripe

      alt Stripe indisponible ou erreur
        Stripe --> Dashboard: ERREUR 503: Stripe unreachable
        deactivate Stripe
        Dashboard -> Logs: Log tentative inscription: Stripe DOWN
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue
        deactivate Logs
        Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Service paiement indisponible
        deactivate Dashboard
      else Paiement OK
        Stripe -> Stripe: 15. Traite paiement et cree subscription

        Stripe --> Dashboard: Paiement confirme + Stripe_ID + Stripe_CustomerID
        deactivate Stripe

        Dashboard -> DB: 16. Cree compte AdminSecretariat (transaction atomique)
        activate DB

        alt Erreur creation (BD)
          DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Transaction echouee
          deactivate DB
          Dashboard -> Stripe: 17. Refund paiement (rollback)
          activate Stripe
          Stripe --> Dashboard: Paiement rembourse
          deactivate Stripe
          Dashboard -> Logs: Log tentative inscription: Creation compte echouee
          activate Logs
          Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue
          deactivate Logs
          Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Erreur serveur, paiement rembourse
          deactivate Dashboard
        else Creation OK
          DB -> DB: 18. INSERT secretariat (nom, TVA, IBAN, date_creation)

          DB -> DB: 19. INSERT user AdminSecretariat (email, pwd_hash, role, secretariat_id, statut ACTIF)

          DB -> DB: 20. INSERT abonnement (secretariat_id, plan, stripe_subscription_id, date_debut, montant_TVAC)

          DB -> DB: 21. INSERT log audit (inscription, email, plan, montant, timestamp, stripe_id)

          DB --> Dashboard: Compte cree avec succes
          deactivate DB

          Dashboard -> Logs: 22. Log event: Nouvel inscrit AdminSecretariat
          activate Logs
          Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
          deactivate Logs

          Dashboard --> A: 23. SUCCES! Compte cree\nPaiement confirme\nVous pouvez maintenant vous connecter
          deactivate Dashboard

          note over A, Logs
            **INSCRIPTION REUSSIE:**
            - Secretariat cree OK
            - AdminSecretariat cree OK
            - Plan: Pro (€XX TVAC/mois)
            - Paiement Stripe confirme
            - DB: Audit logs persistes
            - Logs: Events loggues
            - Acces autorise a partir de maintenant
          end note
        end
      end
    end
  end
end

@enduml
